== Icelandic. ==

English meaning: Rose.

Example sentence: "Ég gaf þér rós" = "I gave you a rose".


Inflection (without definite article):

Hér er: rós

um: rós

frá: rós

til: rósar


With definite article:

hér er: rósin

um: rósina

frá: rósinni

til: rósarinnar


Plural "rósir".


Inflection:

hér eru: rósir

um: rósir

frá: rósum

til: rósa


Inflection with definite article:

hér eru: rósirnar

um: rósirnar

frá: rósunum

til: rósanna


(Hér er/u=here is/are; um=about; frá=from; til=to)